rend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/637946070"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7tLJr5CPzooMEAMaCTEwNDA0NDIyMiClpdisBjAAOBFAJnIJNjM3OTQ2MDcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1704341400.46700", "card_id": "Q_637930542", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 7}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "李在明转到普通病房接受治疗，韩国警方申请批捕嫌犯，有哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中新社首尔 1 月 3 日电 (记者 刘旭) 据韩媒报道，前日遇刺的韩国最大在野党共同民主党党首李在明当地时间 3 日下午从医院的重症监护室转至普通病房，继续接受康复治疗。 本月 2 日，李在明在釜山视察时遇袭，颈内静脉受到损伤。他在釜山大学医院接受紧急治疗后乘坐直升机转至首尔大学医院，接受了包括血栓清除术在内的血管重建术，术后一度转入重症监护室接受治疗。 共同民主党 3 日发布公告称，李在明已根据医嘱于当天 17 时许从重症监护室转到普通病房。 韩联社消息称，共同民主党方面聘请的医学专家在新闻发布会上表示，医疗记录显示，李在明入院初期处于极度危急状态。目前李在明相关指标的检查结果良好，但患者需要维持绝对的安定，不接受任何探视。李在明转到普通病房接受治疗 警方申请批捕嫌犯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fa89741540356b9ff87d3976885116eb_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/637930542"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7tLJr5CPzooMEAMaCTEwNDA0MDc2MyCt5NesBjAAOA5AJ3IJNjM3OTMwNTQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1704341400.48972", "card_id": "Q_637908945", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 92}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "伊朗发生连环爆炸超百人伤亡，哪方势力最有可能此时发动袭击？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1d1ba04d5c68dd454e7197d9c6d8fa26_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/637908945"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI7tLJr5CPzooMEAMaCTEwNDAzNTk2MCC5itasBjAAOJYBQChyCTYzNzkwODk0NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list